    "name": "巴别塔：垂直国度",
    "steam_appid": 3209750,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/d10772b20781331e02118edc067613ec.avif?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=377 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/1c4e4374c42fadd51ffdb2e8047b1e91.webp?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/81acd84514c8c1207bf892c47826bb53.poster.avif?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/81acd84514c8c1207bf892c47826bb53.webm?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/81acd84514c8c1207bf892c47826bb53.mp4?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越风沙、迷雾、雨水、冰雪、晴空和星空六个不同的大气层，突破重力限制，一直向上、向上——直至高塔通天，荣光重铸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/50a1d91dc8e40a0232b163b547f39d32.webp?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/1ca0abe205e911a73d99db20f8e5cb48.poster.avif?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/1ca0abe205e911a73d99db20f8e5cb48.webm?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/1ca0abe205e911a73d99db20f8e5cb48.mp4?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每层塔楼独立储存物资，利用人力搬运、管道运输、热气球转运、大力士抛举…高效调度物资，打造贯通塔身的纵向物流。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/0f00c314a0c3a352d4c8d304bcca4563.webp?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/72463c972ef07b889decacdfa2de0051.poster.avif?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/72463c972ef07b889decacdfa2de0051.webm?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/72463c972ef07b889decacdfa2de0051.mp4?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用斜撑加固塔身，拓展横向空间。近乎悬空的高空花园，或是网状结构般的天空平台。挑战重力限制，撑起天空之城的无限创意。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/0fcf97c651e413f60bcd5bf3871db6f1.webp?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/5394c208f59caa4afeb0169b5a2aceba.poster.avif?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/5394c208f59caa4afeb0169b5a2aceba.webm?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/5394c208f59caa4afeb0169b5a2aceba.mp4?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造仪式平台，将塔民的信念凝聚为改变天象之力，见证呼风唤雨的神迹。回应塔民的心愿，他们将赠予你最珍贵的宝石。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/ec3e2f83cc276a1c222c83d270e421fc.webp?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/696ceb030df8925e435470404d8b8dda.poster.avif?t=1770717858\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/696ceb030df8925e435470404d8b8dda.webm?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209750/extras/696ceb030df8925e435470404d8b8dda.mp4?t=1770717858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攀升途中，塔民将面对信念与天灾的重重考验。点亮奇迹塔身，提振士气与效率。每座奇观都是精神灯塔，若能铸造奇迹，天灾也将为之平息。</p>",
